Paper: hep-th/9409097

Date: 1994-09-16

Title: On the non-relativistic limit of the quantum sine-Gordon model with

integrable boundary conditionAuthors: A.Kapustin, S.Skorik

Comments: 6 pages, CALT-68-1949, USC-94-015

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. A196 (1994) 47-51

We show that the the generalized Calogero-Moser model with boundary potentialof the P\"oschl-Teller type describes the non-relativistic limit of the quantumsine-Gordon model on a half-line with Dirichlet boundary condition.